<div class="center hero-unit">
  <h1>Discography project Task</h1>

  <h2>
    This is the home page for the discography project task.
  </h2>

  <p> Hi fellow programmer, I'm <b>NICOLAU EJARQUE DEU</b> and this is my implementation of the task assigned to prove my Ruby On Rails skills. </p>
  <p> In this task you'll find two resources: <b>Artists</b> and <b>LPs</b>. </p>
