  <h1>LPs:</h1> Currently we have <b><%= @lps%></b> LPs registered. <br/>
  
  <%= link_to "Create LP entry", new_lp_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-success"%> <%= link_to "Check LPs page", lps_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-primary"%>

  <br/>
  
  <div class="center info-text">
    You can check the Artist or LP details by clicking on it's name.<br/>
    You can also edit it's information, delete the entry or even adding new entries by clicking on the appropiate buttons on each page.
  </div>
</div>
